 <p> <span style="color: #2f6443;">JCA Architects is a multi-disciplinary practice seamlessly integrating Architecture, Interiors, Landscape and Urban Design.</span></p>
                                                        <p>Established in 1972 by founding principal and design director JAYANT CHHEDA, it is now headed by Vikesh Chheda & Deodutta Mulye as lead Design Directors. JCA had a modest start designing furniture and conceptual visions in residential and retail interiors in the 1970s. The firm got widespread recognition in the 1980s with revolutionizing designs for commercial and retail spaces. The firm’s constant exploration innovative design strategies and Avant grade responses to client’s needs has resulted in over 1000 commissions ranging from residential and commercial interiors to retail outlets, hospitality and office interiors. The firms foray in Architectural projects involves residential and commercial buildings.</p>
